title: The Symbolism of NFTs
description:
I look at the symbolism of NFTs, how they are related to the margin and chaos, what dangers and opportunities does this offer, and how does this relate to the symbolism of the monster in general. 

Don't forget to back God's'Dog: https://www.godsdog.com

If you're interested in the NFT project, contact us on The Symbolic World website: https://thesymbolicworld.com/contact/
